    "id": "medicaid-montana-rules-2024",
    "name": "Montana Medicaid Eligibility Rules (2024)",
    "description": "Montana-specific Medicaid eligibility rules for 2024. Montana expanded Medicaid under the ACA in 2016, so adults up to 138% FPL are eligible. Coverage is also available for pregnant women, children, and people with disabilities.",
